meta {
  name: Stream SSE
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

post {
  url: {{openemrBaseUrl}}/interface/ask_copilot/stream.php
  body: formUrlEncoded
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: text/event-stream
  Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}
}

body:form-urlencoded {
  csrf_token_form: {{csrfToken}}
  message: Show recent labs
  transcript: []
}

docs {
  ## Gateway SSE (session + CSRF)

  Physician path: browser → OpenEMR only. Proxies hybrid SSE from the LangGraph sidecar
  (`progress` → `clinical` → `citation` → `done`, or `error`).

  - Auth: logged-in OpenEMR session cookie + `csrf_token_form`
  - Client `pid` (if sent) is ignored; bind comes from session
  - Message max length 4000
}
